## ModifyFilesResponse.changed property

Whether any changes were made to the store contents.

**Signature:**

```typescript
changed: boolean;
```

## Remarks

This can only be `false` if [ModifyFilesRequest.allowUnchanged](./hub.modifyfilesrequest.allowunchanged.md) was `true`<!-- -->.
